'''硫酸铽'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Tb<sub>2</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。它可用于合成其它铽化合物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Thermal Analysis and Calorimetry|volume=122|issue=2|language=en|issn=1388-6150|date=2015-11|pages=765–773|doi=10.1007/s10973-015-4786-7|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s10973-015-4786-7|title=Oxysulfate/oxysulfide of Tb3+ obtained by thermal decomposition of terbium sulfate hydrates under different atmospheres|accessdate=2020-04-23|author=R. V. Rodrigues, L. C. Machado, J. R. Matos, E. J. B. Muri, A. A. L. Marins, H. F. Brito, C. A. C. Passos}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Crystal Growth & Design|volume=17|issue=3|language=en|issn=1528-7483|date=2017-03|pages=940–944|doi=10.1021/acs.cgd.6b01541|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.cgd.6b01541|title=Mixed-Lanthanide Metal–Organic Frameworks with Tunable Color and White Light Emission|accessdate=2020-04-23|author=Yanli Gai, Qin Guo, Kecai Xiong, Feilong Jiang, Chenyuan Li, Xin Li, Yan Chen, Chengyuan Zhu, Qing Huang, Rui Yao, Maochun Hong}}</ref>
